                    <div class="h-100 p-4 text-bg-warning rounded-3"> 
                        <h2>Simple Home Hacks</h2>                     
                        <ul>
                            <p class="lead fw-bold">Delicious Mocha (pronounced "moca")</p>
                            <p class="lead fw-bold">Ingredients</p>
                            <li>1 teaspoon finely ground Marere coffee</li>
                            <li>500 ml whole milk</li>
                            <li>2 teaspoons drinking chocolate powder</li>
                            <li>Sugar (optional)</li>
                            <p>Method</p>
                            <li><p class="lead">Bring the milk to a gentle boil.</p></li>
                            <li><p class="lead">Add the finely ground coffee and drinking chocolate powder.</p></li>                       
                            <li><p class="lead">Stir well and sweeten if desired..</p></li>
                            <li><p class="lead">Pour into a glass cup and enjoy your homemade mocha..</p></li>    
                        </ul>                       
                    </div> 
                </div> 
                <div class="col-md-4"> 
                    <div class="h-100 p-4 bg-body-tertiary border rounded-3"> 
                        <h2>Simple Home Hacks cont...</h2>                                         
                        <ul> 
                            <p class="lead fw-bold">Thick Banana Smoothie</p>
                            <p class="lead fw-bold">Ingredients</p>
                            <li>3 ripe bananas</li>
                            <li>300 ml milk</li>
                            <li>2 ice cubes</li>
                            <li>½ teaspoon chia seeds (optional)</li>
                            <li>2 drops vanilla essence (optional)</li>
                            <p>Method</p>
                            <li><p class="lead">Peel and slice the bananas.</p></li>
                            <li><p class="lead">Place them in a ziplock bag or sealed container and freeze overnight.</p></li>                       
                            <li><p class="lead">In a blender, add milk and ice cubes.</p></li>                                                                    
                        </ul>                                           
                    </div> 
                </div> 
                <div class="col-md-4"> 
                    <div class="h-100 p-5 text-bg-secondary rounded-3"> 
                        <ul> 
                            <li><p class="lead">Add the frozen bananas, chia seeds, and vanilla.</p></li>  
                            <li><p class="lead">Blend for 90 seconds until smooth and creamy.</p></li>  
                            <li><p class="lead">Pour into your favorite glass and enjoy the delicious, thick texture.</p></li> 
                            <li><p class="lead">In a blender, add milk and ice cubes.</p></li>
                            <li><p class="lead">Add the frozen bananas, chia seeds, and vanilla.</p></li>  
                            <li><p class="lead">Blend for 90 seconds until smooth and creamy.</p></li>  
                            <li><p class="lead">Pour into your favorite glass and enjoy the delicious, thick texture.</p></li>                                      
                        </ul>
